OL,3,CCampaigners demand compensation as
OL,4,C'our children's lives are slipping
OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FCampaigners have handed in a petition
OL,8,Fcalling on the Government to provide
OL,9,Fcompensation for victims of an
OL,10,Fepilepsy drug that caused infants to
OL,11,Fbe born with birth defects as "our
OL,12,Fchildren's lives are slipping away".
OL,14,FMothers who were prescribed the drug
OL,15,FSodium Valproate during pregnancy had
OL,16,Fnever been warned of the risks to
OL,17,Ftheir unborn children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
