OL,3,CCampaigners demand compensation as
OL,4,C'our children's lives are slipping
OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FThe medication has been successfully
OL,8,Fused to treat epilepsy and bipolar
OL,9,Fdisorder and also prevents migraines,
OL,10,Fbut it has also been linked to birth
OL,11,Fdefects in thousands of babies.
OL,13,FCampaigners are calling for an end to
OL,14,Fthe delays in compensation, which the
OL,15,Fgovernment has been considering for
OL,16,Fseveral years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
