OL,3,CCampaigners demand compensation as
OL,4,C'our children's lives are slipping
OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fspokesperson say it is a "complex area
OL,9,Fof work and the government is
OL,10,Fcarefully considering the Patient
OL,11,FSafety Commissioner's recommendations
OL,12,Fin full."
OL,14,FSymptoms of those born with Foetal
OL,15,FValproate Spectrum Disorder include
OL,16,Flearning difficulties, speech and
OL,17,Flanguage delay, sensory processing
OL,18,Fdisorder, heart and kidney defects,
OL,19,Fand deformation of the spine or limbs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
