OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FAn independent review, chaired by
OL,8,FBaroness Julia Cumberlege and launched
OL,9,Fin 2020, strongly criticised the
OL,10,Findustry and recommended that the
OL,11,FGovernment set up a redress scheme to
OL,12,Fcompensate all affected children and
OL,13,Ftheir families.
OL,15,FIn 2024, another report, by the
OL,16,FPatient Safety Commissioner Dr
OL,17,FHenrietta Hughes, set out exactly how
OL,18,Fthe compensation scheme could work,
OL,19,Fand suggested the Government make
OL,20,Fquicker interim payments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
