OL,4,C'our children's lives are slipping
OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FNone of the families affected by the
OL,8,Fdrug have yet to receive a payment.
OL,10,FEmma Murphy and Janet Williams, who
OL,11,Fhave helped to lead the campaign for
OL,12,FSodium Valproate compensation, were
OL,13,Famong those at Parliament on
OL,14,FWednesday, 10 September.
OL,16,FThey desperately want to see action
OL,17,Ffrom the government after both raising
OL,18,Fdisabled children who were exposed to
OL,19,FSodium Valproate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
