OL,3,CCampaigners demand compensation as
OL,4,C'our children's lives are slipping
OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FEmma Murphy said: "It shows the
OL,8,Fimportance of compensating families.
OL,9,FWe've now had two government backed
OL,10,Freviews, we've had cross party support
OL,11,Ffrom the whole of parliament, and yet
OL,12,Fagain we are still waiting.
OL,14,F"Civil servants seem to be blocking
OL,15,Fthis and it is disgraceful that
OL,16,Ffamilies across the country are still
OL,17,Fwaiting.
OL,19,F"We shouldn't have to be here bringing
OL,20,Fdisabled children to Number 10 Downing
OL,21,FStreet."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
