OL,3,CCampaigners demand compensation as
OL,4,C'our children's lives are slipping
OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FJanet Williams added: "We understand
OL,8,Fthe position that the government are
OL,9,Fin with this. Financially, we totally
OL,10,Funderstand. However, they've got to
OL,11,Funderstand the position of the parents
OL,12,Ffinancially too.
OL,14,F"They need to recognise the damage
OL,15,Fthat this is causing. We know children
OL,16,Fwho have already died through this."
OL,18,FSodium valproate has been linked to
OL,19,Flifelong disabilities in at least
OL,20,F20,000 babies whose mothers were
OL,21,Fprescribed the drug during pregnancy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
