OL,4,C'our children's lives are slipping
OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,FJade Wright, from Lancashire, is the
OL,8,Fmother-of-three children, all born
OL,9,Fwith signs of Foetal Valproate
OL,10,FSyndrome. Her eldest son Tyler is the
OL,11,Fworst affected.
OL,13,FJoining the campaigners in London, she
OL,14,Fsaid: "This scandal is so awful, it is
OL,15,Fso massive and it has taken so much
OL,16,Faway from our family.
OL,18,F"Every day that this compensation is
OL,19,Fdelayed, more people are suffering.
OL,20,FPeople can't wait anymore. People are
OL,21,Fdying."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
