OL,5,Caway'
OL,7,F"We've had no answers. It feels like
OL,8,Fthey're trying to sweep us under the
OL,9,Frug.
OL,11,F"It's painful. All of this damage that
OL,12,Fthey've caused is like we don't
OL,13,Fmatter."
OL,15,FJade's message to the government is
OL,16,Fsimple: "Start compensation payments.
OL,17,FThis can't be delayed anymore.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
