OL,7,F"Act now and support these families.
OL,8,FWe need financial redress and non
OL,9,Ffinancial redress. We need support
OL,10,Fthere because our children's lives are
OL,11,Fslipping away. They need to act and do
OL,12,Fsomething now."
OL,14,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "The harm caused by
OL,16,Fsodium valproate continues to be felt
OL,17,Ftoday.
